December 26, 2019    Gift Day * Friday, December 27, 2019    Gift Day * Monday, December 30, 2019    Gift Day * Tuesday, December 31, 2019    New Year’s Day Holiday Wednesday, January 1, 2020    Martin Luther King Day Monday, January 20, 2020    Memorial Day Holiday Monday, May 25, 2020    Plus    Two Floating Holidays          Holiday Details   *This schedule grants three (3) gift days and one (1) excused/gift day over the December/January holiday break. Employees do not use any accrued leave benefits during this time.      GROUP B  Applies to all employees working in essential units, including but not limited to the University of Illinois Hospital and Clinics; Biologic Resources Laboratory; units reporting to the Vice Chancellor for Student Affairs, including Campus Auxiliary Services (CAS) Administration, CAS Facilities, Campus Housing, Counseling Center, Dean of Students, Dining Services, Dorin Forum, Student Affairs IT, Student Centers, Credit Union I Arena (formerly the UIC Pavilion), and the Office of the Vice Chancellor for Student Affairs; Academic Computing and Communications Center (ACCC); Telecommunication Services; and units reporting to the Office of the Vice Chancellor for Administrative Services, including Facilities Management, Capital Programs, Parking Services, Environmental Health and Safety, Facility and Space Planning, and the UIC Police Department:      Group B Holidays      HOLIDAYS DAYS OBSERVED      Independence Day Holiday Thursday, July 4, 2019    Labor Day Holiday Monday, September 2, 2019    Thanksgiving Day Thursday, November 28, 2019    Half Gift/Half Excused Day * Tuesday, December 24, 2019    Christmas Day Holiday Wednesday, December 25, 2019    Gift Day * Friday, December 27, 2019    Gift Day * Monday, December 30, 2019    Gift Day * Tuesday, December 31, 2019    New Year’s Day Holiday Observed Wednesday, January 1, 2020    Martin Luther King Day Monday, January 20, 2020    Memorial Day Holiday Monday, May 25, 2020    Plus    Four Floating Holidays          Holiday Details   * This schedule grants three (3) gift days and one (1) excused/gift day over the December/January holiday break. Group B employees of the UI Hospital & Clinics will receive the gift days as additional floating holidays that may be used any time between December 27, 2019, and June 30, 2020, with supervisor approval. All other Group B employees required to work on the gift days may schedule alternate days off between December 1, 2019 and June 30, 2020.     Please contact Susan Balmes (balmes@uic.edu) or Joanna Wolek (jwolek@uic.edu) if you have any questions or need further information.                    UIC Logo         Human  Resources           Related Links    Faculty Affairs    UI Health HR    Student Employment    Office for Access and Equity    Office of International Services    Office of Business and Financial Services    University of Illinois Board of Trustees (BOT)      TOOLS    EDDIE    HR Reporting Portal    My UI Info        Footer Button Menu    Holiday Schedule    College Contacts List    Job Aids    Payroll Schedules    Template Letters    University Policy Library    Site Login    UIC HR Remote Access    UICHR Webmail         Contact   UIC Human Resources  uichrwelcomecenter@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts             UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 2.38.0  © 2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois |  Privacy Statement    Campuses   University of Illinois System  Urbana-Champaign  Springfield      Cookie Settings                   